author: Kathleen Pender
title: S.F.’s SoFi lands whopping $1 billion in venture capital
text:
Photo: SoFi CEO Mike Cagney says SoFi plans to expand. CEO Mike Cagney says SoFi plans to expand.
Social Finance Inc., a marketplace lender based in San Francisco, confirmed Wednesday that it has received $1 billion in venture capital from existing investors, led by SoftBank Group. CEO Mike Cagney says SoFi plans to expand. CEO Mike Cagney says SoFi plans to expand.
